    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_52_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2407_02_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "橋本さんの提案で、星見プロからみんなに\n誕生日プレゼントとして慰安旅行を計画したんだ",
      "startTime": 3.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_52_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2407_02_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "旅行先は俺の方で考えようと思っているけれど\nもし、希望があったら受け付けるよ",
      "startTime": 11.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_52_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2407_02_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "グループは誕生日が近い人達で組ませてもらったが……\n日頃の疲れを存分に癒して来てくれ！",
      "startTime": 17.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_52_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2407_02_01-ngs001.m4a",
      "text": "え？",
      "startTime": 20.6040805817,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_52_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2407_02_01-aoi001.m4a",
      "text": "え？",
      "startTime": 21.2976602852,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_52_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2407_02_01-rio001.m4a",
      "text": "ええ？",
      "startTime": 22.1040758132,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_52_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2407_02_01-kor001.m4a",
      "text": "はあ？",
      "startTime": 23.037408765,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_52_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2407_02_01-mei001.m4a",
      "text": "わーい！",
      "startTime": 24.070742607,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawabeach-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――星見プロ誕生日慰安旅行in沖縄",
      "startTime": 27.1707422891,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_coast-01.m4a",
          "delay": 1833.3388647999982,
          "startTime": 29.0040811539
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-coast-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 2133.335685799999,
          "startTime": 29.3040779749
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawabeach-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_52_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2407_02_01-mei002.m4a",
      "text": "わーい、海だー！　ねーねー早くみんなで遊びに\n行こうよ！　あ、見て見て！　あっちに屋台も出てる！",
      "startTime": 34.8374113082,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-coast-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 5202.384456100006,
          "startTime": 40.0397957643
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawabeach-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_52_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2407_02_01-ngs002.m4a",
      "text": "あ、芽衣ちゃん！　{user}さんが\nチェックイン終わるまでもう少しここで待ってよ？",
      "startTime": 42.7707478206,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawabeach-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_52_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2407_02_01-rio002.m4a",
      "text": "まさか{user}さんも付いてくるなんてね\nてっきり私達だけで行くのかと思ってたわ",
      "startTime": 51.3040811539,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawabeach-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_52_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2407_02_01-kor002.m4a",
      "text": "私達の誕生日は口実で、単に彼が\n休みたかっただけなんじゃない？",
      "startTime": 58.9040811539,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawabeach-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_52_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2407_02_01-mei003.m4a",
      "text": "芽衣は{user}さんも一緒に来てくれて\n嬉しいけどなー。人数多い方が楽しいもん！",
      "startTime": 63.9374144872,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_52_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2407_02_01-ngs003.m4a",
      "text": "本当はさとみさんが付いてくるはずだったんですけど\n楽しみにし過ぎて前日に熱を出しちゃったらしくて……",
      "startTime": 72.4707478206,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawabeach-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_52_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2407_02_01-aoi002.m4a",
      "text": "可哀そうだけど、なんだかさとみらしいね\n次の機会があれば一緒に来られるといいな",
      "startTime": 81.3040811539,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawabeach-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_52_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2407_02_01-kor003.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ……次なんてないわよ。なんで毎年あなた達と\n旅行になんて行かなきゃいけないのよ",
      "startTime": 89.9374144872,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawabeach-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_52_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2407_02_01-aoi003.m4a",
      "text": "そんなこと言ってるけど{user}君に\n「旅行先は沖縄がいい」って言ったのは君じゃないか",
      "startTime": 95.970745786,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_52_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2407_02_01-kor004.m4a",
      "text": "どーせ断ったって強制的に参加させられるんだから\n自分の希望を言うくらい構わないでしょ？",
      "startTime": 103.770745786,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawabeach-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_52_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2407_02_01-rio003.m4a",
      "text": "うちの事務所が強制参加させることはないと思うわよ\n行きたくないなら欠席でも良かったんじゃない？",
      "startTime": 111.070745786,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawabeach-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_52_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2407_02_01-kor005.m4a",
      "text": "ちょ、うるさいわね！　福利厚生を受けないと損だと\n思っただけよ！　以上！",
      "startTime": 118.0040775935,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawabeach-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_52_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2407_02_01-ngs004.m4a",
      "text": "franさん……飛行機の隣の席で\n凄く楽しそうに沖縄の観光雑誌を見てたような～……？",
      "startTime": 124.5040775935,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_52_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2407_02_01-mei004.m4a",
      "text": "昨日、kanaちゃんのSNSでも「浮足立ちの\nfranちゃん」って写真付きの投稿見たような……",
      "startTime": 133.8040857315,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawabeach-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_52_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2407_02_01-aoi004.m4a",
      "text": "なんだ、franにも可愛いところがあるじゃないか",
      "startTime": 138.0707396188,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawabeach-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_52_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2407_02_01-kor006.m4a",
      "text": "あーもう！　別にいいでしょ！　あんた達はあんた達で\n楽しみなさい！　私も一人で勝手に楽しむから。じゃあ",
      "startTime": 146.0040806453,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawabeach-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawabeach-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_52_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2407_02_01-mei005.m4a",
      "text": "えぇー！　franちゃんだけ別行動するの……？\nせっかくみんなで来たんだからみんなで遊ぼうよ！",
      "startTime": 154.3374190648,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawabeach-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_52_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2407_02_01-rio004.m4a",
      "text": "一応会社のお金で来てるんだし。私達と一緒に\n居たら色々と経費で落ちるかもしれないわね",
      "startTime": 162.3707523982,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawabeach-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_52_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2407_02_01-mei006.m4a",
      "text": "それってタダってこと！？",
      "startTime": 166.0707548776,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawabeach-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
